## Update Candidate

```http
PUT https://api.teamtailor.com/v1/candidates/1337 HTTP/1.1
X-Api-Version: <%= config[:api_version] %>
Authorization: Token token=abc123abc123

{
  "data": {
    "id": "1337",
    "attributes": {
      "first-name": "Update"
    },
    "type": "candidates"
  }
}
```

```shell
curl -X "PUT" "https://api.teamtailor.com/v1/candidates/1337" \
    -H "Content-Type: application/vnd.api+json" \
    -H "X-Api-Version: <%= config[:api_version] %>"
    -H "Authorization: Token token=abc123abc123" \
    -d $'{ "data": { "id": "1337", "attributes": { "first-name": "David" }, "type": "candidates" } }'
```

